headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Start Seeing Double with Bonuses on Acid Lab Sell Missions
content:
Help the Fooliganz dose the world by offloading your supply of potent psychedelics in Acid Sell Missions, paying out 2X GTA$ & RP through September 13.

Get your psychedelics business up to snuff with 40% off all Acid Lab Upgrades and Modifications.

The MTL Brickade 6x6 service vehicle that's necessary to initiate your acid production endeavors is also 40% off at Warstock Cache & Carry.
